# This git repo is rooted at the MQL5/ folder but tracks ONLY the
# "Alligator + Heiken Ashi EA" project, so the repo mirrors the live MT5
# layout (Experts/Alligator_Heiken_Ashi_EA/ + Scripts/Alligator_Heiken_Ashi_EA_Tests/).
# Everything else under MQL5/ (other EAs, indicators, the standard Include/,
# Files/, Logs/, Profiles/, experts.dat, ...) is ignored.

# 1) Ignore everything at the MQL5 root, then re-include just what we want.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/Experts/
!/Scripts/

# 2) Inside Experts/ — only our project folder.
/Experts/*
!/Experts/Alligator_Heiken_Ashi_EA/

# 3) Inside Scripts/ — only our tests folder.
/Scripts/*
!/Scripts/Alligator_Heiken_Ashi_EA_Tests/

# 4) Within the tracked folders: ignore build artifacts, runtime state,
#    and the large/transient Strategy-Tester dumps.
*.ex5
EA_State*.json
*.tmp
journel*.txt
journal*.txt
*ReportTester*.xlsx
*ReportTester*.htm*
*ReportOptimizer*.xml
*ReportOptimizer*.htm*
